Hello! Thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides, the finest bowling alley in town. My name is Alex. Could I get your name, please?

Hi Alex, I'm Jamie.

Nice to meet you, Jamie. How can I assist you with your billing issue today?

I noticed an unusual charge on my bill and wanted to clarify it.

I'd be happy to help with that. Could I first have your billing account number, please?

Sure, it's six seven eight nine four three zero one two.

Thank you, Jamie. Could you also confirm the last four digits of the phone number associated with your account?

Yes, it's five nine five four.

Great, thank you for that information. I'll take a look at your account and review the charges for you.

I see the charge in question, and I can confirm it was an error. We'll remove that charge from your account immediately.

Thank you so much, Alex!

You're welcome, Jamie. Thank you for your patience. If you have any more questions, feel free to call us back. Have a great day!
